latest tweeted video message, <a href="https://www.fxstreet.com/economic-calendar/united-states">US</a> President Donald Trump sounds optimistic about getting the coronavirus (COVID-19) vaccine just after the election in November. The Republican leader also mentioned that he feels perfect now while seeing the virus as a blessing for him.</p>\n\n<div class="twitter_cke fxs_external">\n<blockquote align="center" class="twitter-tweet" data-dnt="true">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en">A MESSAGE FROM THE PRESIDENT! <a href="https://t.co/uhLIcknAjT">pic.twitter.com/uhLIcknAjT</a></p>\n&mdash; Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump) <a href="https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1313959702104023047?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 7, 2020</a></blockquote>\n<script async="" charset="utf-8" src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js"></script></div>\n\n<h2 class="fxs_headline_medium">Key quotes</h2>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>Felt great almost immediately after Regeneron.</p>\n\n<p>For me it wasn&#39;t therapeutic, it made me better; I call it a cure, will make it free to use.</p>\n\n<p>We have many companies that are in the final stages.</p>\n\n<p>We&#39;re going to have a very great vaccine shortly.</p>\n\n<p>I think we should have it before the election but frankly the politics gets involved and that&#39;s ok, they want to play their games, so it&#39;s going to be right after the election.</p>\n\n<p>FDA is approving things in weeks that used to take years.</p>\n\n<p>I feel like, perfect.</p>\n\n<p>This was China&#39;s fault, they&#39;re going to pay a big price.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<h3 class="fxs_headline_medium">Market implications</h3>\n\n<p>Although the news favors the market&rsquo;s risk-on sentiment, S&amp;P 500 Futures begin Thursday&rsquo;s moves nearly unchanged above 3,400. The reason for inactivity could be traces from traders&rsquo; cautious mood ahead of the US Vice Presidential Debate, up at 01:00 GMT.</p>\n\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <!-- Disclaimer in post! -->\r\n            <div class="fxs_disclaimer_block">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Information on these pages contains forward-looking statements that involve risks and uncertainties.
